 the lattice theta parameter. We provide quantitative results\nfor how the topological charge `freezes' with decreasing lattice spacing and\nwith increasing N, and show how we cicumvent this issue in our calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2021 10:17:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 16:55:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Dec 2021 18:12:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
