f several susceptible classes, this\ngeneralizes to (5.10); in a future paper, we will show that (3.8), (5.10) may\nbe used to obtain approximate control policies which compare well with the\noptimal control of the original model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2021 11:06:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-30"}
